OL,3,CNumber of skilled worker permits
OL,4,Cissued in Jersey triples in four years
OL,6,FThe number of skilled worker permits
OL,7,Fin has nearly tripled in the past four
OL,8,Fyears, ITV News can reveal.
OL,10,FHospitality bosses have told ITV News
OL,11,Fthat's because they are having to hire
OL,12,Fmore people on those skilled worker
OL,13,Fpermits, which can be more expensive,
OL,14,Fbecause the temporary permit system is
OL,15,Ftoo restrictive.
OL,17,FThey said they needed more flexibility
OL,18,Fin the temporary scheme to avoid
OL,19,Fhaving to resort to more skilled
OL,20,Fpermits just to retain staff.
