OL,6,FThe permits, which can allow
OL,7,Findividuals to bring dependants with
OL,8,Fthem, have risen from 265 in 2020 to
OL,9,F754 in 2023.
OL,11,FThe Sustainable Economic Development
OL,12,FMinister, Deputy Kirsten Morel, has
OL,13,Fmet with representatives of the
OL,14,Findustry and said they "could do with
OL,15,Fchanges on those permit rules".
OL,17,FHe committed to working with the Home
OL,18,FAffairs Minister to address the issue.
