OL,6,FThe data also shows the number of
OL,7,Ftemporary work permits has risen by
OL,8,F3280% since 2019, increasing from 67
OL,9,Fto 2265 in 2023.
OL,11,FDeputy Morel said part of that
OL,12,Fincrease was caused by Brexit, which
OL,13,Fhad a major impact on the permit
OL,14,Fsystem with businesses no longer able
OL,15,Fto rely on the European workforce.
OL,17,FCurrently hospitality bosses have a
OL,18,Fnumber of options when bringing in
OL,19,Fstaff:
OL,21,FNine month temporary permits:
