OL,6,F"One person here on a skilled permit,
OL,7,Fwho wanted to remain anonymous, said
OL,8,Fthe temporary system was "frustrating
OL,9,Ffor both employee and employer".
OL,11,FThey added: "Through skilled work
OL,12,Fpermits, my dependents are allowed to
OL,13,Fjoin me and that's an open door for my
OL,14,Fdaughter to get the best British
OL,15,Feducation compared to the type of
OL,16,Feducation we have in Kenya."
OL,18,FThe Head of Jersey Hospitality
OL,19,FAssociation, Marcus Calvani, told ITV
OL,20,FNews he had previously warned the
OL,21,Fgovernment about the issue.
